#      /api/services (status via TCP) + /api/services/{name}/restart (admin, systemctl Linux).
#      Logic o quickwin.dev/servicemanager. UI: tab Services trong OpenITMS.vue.
# WHAT: file MOI api/quickwin_services.go (list+restart, addr tu config/env); router.go +1 dong;
#      go.mod +servicemanager; OpenITMS.vue +tab Services (data-table status + nut Restart).
#      Rebase: them registerQuickwinServices sau registerQuickwinRegistry + tab thu 4 trong OpenITMS.vue.
# SPEC: docs/L2-specs/core-patches/0007-service-manager.md
# BASELINE: v2.18.16
#
